       rolemaps-to="P"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Nicotinamide Adenine Dinucleotide is a major electron acceptor in the oxidation of fuel molecules. The reactive part of Nicotinamide Adenine Dinucleotide is its nictinamide ring, a pyridine derivate.
    </text>
